{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/WideFiresShort.gif?t=1735267929\" /><i><strong>Fire Isle</strong></i> is a high-energy, competitive multiplayer game where up to four players wield unique flames to battle for control of a dynamic, ever-changing map. The objective? Dominate the battlefield by collecting <strong><i>Wisps</i></strong>, ethereal flames that appear randomly across the map. Be the first to burn their tiles - or risk losing them when they move  after a set number of turns. As resources grow scarce and strategies collide, only the most cunning fires will survive!<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/AboutGameWisps2.png?t=1735267929\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/MultiHeader.png?t=1735267929\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/BlockingOutTrue.gif?t=1735267929\" />Hone your skills in solo mode or take the chaos online with up to 4 players. Box out your rivals, claim the most tiles, and collect Wisps until the strongest Fire wins! With its fast-paced gameplay, ever-shifting strategies, and chaotic item mechanics, <i><strong>Fire Isle</strong></i> is a must-play for anyone who loves intense multiplayer action against their friends.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/HeaderItems_Abilities.png?t=1735267929\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/Gameplay2.gif?t=1735267929\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Sparks</strong></i> fuel your fire, but <strong><i>Ashes</i></strong> fuel your ambitions. Use them to unleash devastating abilities, secure powerful upgrades, or sabotage your rivals.\u00a0The <strong><i>Item Box </i></strong>on the other hand<strong><i>,</i></strong> adds an unpredictable edge to every match. Spin the wheel and seize the advantage:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Spark Unlock</i></strong> removes your <strong><i>Spark Cap</i></strong> for a limited time, letting you unleash your full potential.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Cold Front</i></strong> freezes your rivals\u2019 progress by spiking their tile costs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Flame Umbrella</i></strong> shields you from the brutal dowsing effects of rain.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>#1 Extinguisher</strong>\u00a0singles out your greatest rival, stacking to cripple the leading player's firepower!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2026and plenty of others to keep the heat on!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/HeaderWisps.png?t=1735267929\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Burn fast, burn smart! <strong><i>Wisps</i></strong> are the key to victory, and claiming them requires both speed and precision. Gather enough <strong><i>Ashes</i></strong>, and you can even purchase extra <strong><i>Wisps</i></strong> to turn the tide in your favor.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/HeaderTerrain.png?t=1735267929\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/EndCap.gif?t=1735267929\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Always keep the Isle's terrain in mind, it's as unpredictable as your opponents! Ignite <i><strong>Coal Deposits</strong></i>, erupt <i><strong>Volcanoes</strong></i>, and even spend <i><strong>Ashes</strong></i> to burn through <i><strong>Snow</strong></i>, <i><strong>Sand</strong></i>, and <i><strong>Mountains</strong></i>, adapting your strategy as resources continue to dwindle.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735267929","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/page.bg.jpg?t=1735267929","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/c8848edd8f56edaa356fd518cab986871f9cb3a7/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735267929","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/c8848edd8f56edaa356fd518cab986871f9cb3a7/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735267929","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/WideFiresShort.gif?t=1735267929\" /><i><strong>Fire Isle</strong></i> is a high-energy, competitive multiplayer game where up to four players wield unique flames to battle for control of a dynamic, ever-changing map. The objective? Dominate the battlefield by collecting <strong><i>Wisps</i></strong>, ethereal flames that appear randomly across the map. Be the first to burn their tiles - or risk losing them when they move  after a set number of turns. As resources grow scarce and strategies collide, only the most cunning fires will survive!<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/AboutGameWisps2.png?t=1735267929\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/MultiHeader.png?t=173526