g class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/HeaderWisps.png?t=1735267929\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Burn fast, burn smart! <strong><i>Wisps</i></strong> are the key to victory, and claiming them requires both speed and precision. Gather enough <strong><i>Ashes</i></strong>, and you can even purchase extra <strong><i>Wisps</i></strong> to turn the tide in your favor.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/HeaderTerrain.png?t=1735267929\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/extras/EndCap.gif?t=1735267929\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Always keep the Isle's terrain in mind, it's as unpredictable as your opponents! Ignite <i><strong>Coal Deposits</strong></i>, erupt <i><strong>Volcanoes</strong></i>, and even spend <i><strong>Ashes</strong></i> to burn through <i><strong>Snow</strong></i>, <i><strong>Sand</strong></i>, and <i><strong>Mountains</strong></i>, adapting your strategy as resources continue to dwindle.</p>","developers":["SneezeDev"],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093990/header.jpg?t=1735267929","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257054900,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257054900/movie480.mp4?t=1727906653","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257054900/movie_max.mp4?t=1727906653"},"name":"Fire Is